<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Reserva cancelada</title>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f4f4; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">

<table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"
       style="max-width: 600px; background-color: #ffffff; margin: 40px auto; border-radius: 8px;
              box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); overflow: hidden;">

    <!-- Header -->
    <tr>
        <td style="background-color: #4f46e5; padding: 20px 40px; text-align: center;">
            <div style="display: inline-block;">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="#ffffff" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                     width="40" height="40" style="vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 10px;">
                    <path d="M19 4h-3a2 2 0 00-2-2H8a2 2 0 00-2 2H4a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2h16a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2zm-1 2v12H6V6h12zM9 10h6v2H9v-2zm0 4h6v2H9v-2z"/>
                </svg>
                <span style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; color: #ffffff;">AgendApp</span>
            </div>
        </td>
    </tr>

    <!-- Content -->
    <tr>
        <td style="padding: 30px 40px;">
            <h2 style="color: #333333; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 25px;">Reserva cancelada</h2>

            <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #333333; line-height: 1.6;">
                Hola <strong>{{professionalName}}</strong>,
            </p>

            <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #333333; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 25px;">
                La siguiente reserva ha sido cancelada:
            </p>

            <table width="100%" cellpadding="8" cellspacing="0"
                   style="border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 15px; color: #333333; margin-bottom: 30px;">
                <tr>
                    <td style="width: 30%; font-weight: bold;">Cliente:</td>
                    <td>{{clientName}}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="background-color: #f9f9f9;">
                    <td style="font-weight: bold;">Email:</td>
                    <td>{{clientEmail}}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="font-weight: bold;">Teléfono:</td>
                    <td>{{clientPhoneNumber}}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="background-color: #f9f9f9;">
                    <td style="font-weight: bold;">Servicio:</td>
                    <td>{{serviceName}}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="font-weight: bold;">Fecha:</td>
                    <td>{{date}}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="background-color: #f9f9f9;">
                    <td style="font-weight: bold;">Hora:</td>
                    <td>{{time}}</td>
                </tr>
            </table>

            <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #777777; text-align: center;">
                Recordá revisar tus próximas reservas para mantener la agenda actualizada.
            </p>

            <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #eeeeee; margin: 30px 0;" />

            <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #999999; text-align: center;">
                © {{currentYear}} AgendApp. Todos los derechos reservados.
            </p>
        </td>
    </tr>

</table>

</body>
</html>
